https://dx.doi.org/10.4135/9781529730739;
https://doi.org/10.1093/heapol/czs088;
https://doi.org/10.1007/978-3-319-00104-3_3). This shift has led to the rise of holistic health approaches over the past decade, including EcoHealth, One Health, and more recently, Planetary Health…”
